1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:48,207
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:55,932 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 1=

11
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,239
Help!

12
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:05,760
Don't run!

13
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,000
- Stop!
- Don't run!

14
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:07,879
Help!

15
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:08,879
- Stop!
- Don't you run!

16
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:09,760
Stop there!

17
00:01:10,719 --> 00:01:11,280
Help!

18
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,280
Trying to run?

19
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:36,519
Run, huh?

20
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:38,719
(Jia Zhengdao, Gu Group)
Thought you could run, huh?

21
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,079
Well...

22
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,359
If you can get away under our noses,

23
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:48,120
what happens to Gu Group's reputation?

24
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,640
B-Boss, I...

25
00:01:50,079 --> 00:01:51,560
If I'd known this was so risky,

26
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,959
I'd never have come, I swear!

27
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,680
Look,

28
00:01:58,159 --> 00:02:00,120
jump from here right now.

29
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,879
If you can still get back up,

30
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:04,799
I'll let you go.

31
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,199
No guts?

32
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,879
Boss, please...

33
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,960
You guys, help him a bit, okay?

34
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:20,520
Wait!

35
00:02:20,719 --> 00:02:21,560
Boss, please!

36
00:02:21,719 --> 00:02:22,680
Spare me!

37
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:24,719
I was wrong, boss!

38
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:25,360
Go down.

39
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:46,000
This mortal body...

40
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:48,159
can rival the gods.

41
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,199
Divine power.

42
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,919
You ants,

43
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,080
how dare you act up!

44
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,438
(Su Wubing,
Reincarnation of Immortal King)

45
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,439
This is...?

46
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,960
Ten thousand years later...

47
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:37,960
The Heavenly Dao
still carries such might?

48
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:44,039
Ningxue, I'm coming to save you!

49
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:47,919
Today is a big day in Fan City.

50
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,920
The Gus and Lins are joining together.

51
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:50,800
(Lin Ningxue, Holy Maiden; Gu Yuanbing)
The Gus and Lins are joining together.

52
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,240
(Lin Ningxue, Holy Maiden; Gu Yuanbing)

53
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,120
(Lin Ningxue, Holy Maiden; Gu Yuanbing)
What's more,

54
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,479
(Lin Ningxue, Holy Maiden; Gu Yuanbing)

55
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:53,730
(Lin Ningxue, Holy Maiden; Gu Yuanbing)
that Young Master Gu and Miss Lin

56
00:03:53,730 --> 00:03:53,840
that Young Master Gu and Miss Lin

57
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:56,759
are truly a perfect match.

58
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,879
Mr. Gu Yuanbing,

59
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:02,199
do you take Miss Lin Ningxue
as your wife,

60
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:04,840
for better or worse,

61
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:06,560
for richer or poorer,

62
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:10,639
faithful for life?

63
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:14,960
I do.

64
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,680
Miss Lin Ningxue,

65
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:19,319
do you take Mr. Gu Yuanbing
as your husband,

66
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,839
through thick and thin,

67
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,600
standing by his side,

68
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:27,199
till death do you part?

69
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,079
Why isn't Miss Lin
saying anything?

70
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,240
Could it be a forced marriage?

71
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:41,920
Ningxue.

72
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:44,480
Your father's waiting for us.

73
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,920
(For my father...)

74
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,759
(this is the only way.)

75
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:54,879
I...

76
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,000
I do.

77
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,079
Ningxue.

78
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,680
I promised you

79
00:05:37,319 --> 00:05:38,199
that no matter how far,

80
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,360
I'd find you.

81
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:47,000
(Who exactly are you?)

82
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:52,639
Who are you?

83
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,560
How dare you crash my wedding?

84
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,920
Where'd this punk come from?

85
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,600
How dare you cause trouble
for Young Master Gu!

86
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,160
Who is that guy?

87
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,279
Where did he pop out from?

88
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:01,759
Who cares?

89
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,199
This is about to get interesting.

90
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:04,319
(Shan Yingying,
Apprentice in the Martial Hall)

91
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,199
(Shan Yingying, Martial Hall Apprentice)
Why is it him?

92
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,519
Didn't I send my senior?

93
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:11,004
(Two Hours Earlier)

94
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:14,560
Ningxue, you can't marry him.

95
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,839
You know what kind of man

96
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,680
Gu Yuanbing is.

97
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:17,680
Yingying...

98
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:20,439
You know I have no choice.

99
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,199
Two years ago,

100
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:26,360
my dad suddenly fell ill.

101
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,680
Even our family's Longevity Pill

102
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:33,240
can barely keep him hanging on.

103
00:06:34,759 --> 00:06:35,560
Now...

104
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:39,480
only the miracle cure in
Gu Yuanbing's hands

105
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,720
can save him.

106
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,360
But what if that medicine's a scam?

107
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,560
What if he's lying to you?

108
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,040
For my dad's life,

109
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,560
I'll take that risk.

110
00:06:58,079 --> 00:06:58,720
If that's the case...

111
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:01,839
then

112
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:05,160
after you get the medicine,

113
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,839
I'll ask senior to take you away.

114
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:11,319
Will that really work?

115
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,639
Where did this idiot come from?

116
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:15,240
Daring to stir trouble
at Mr. Gu's wedding!

117
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,199
Throw him out!

118
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:17,720
Yes!

119
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:28,399
(Since when did this city
have someone like that?)

120
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:29,959
Ningxue.

121
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:32,319
Come with me.

122
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,800
I'll explain everything.

123
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:35,720
Wait.

124
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:43,199
Ningxue.

125
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,920
The miracle cure...

126
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:46,720
is still with me.

127
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,519
Your father's illness...

128
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:57,480
Let's go.

129
00:07:59,560 --> 00:07:59,959
What?

130
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:01,800
They're just leaving?

131
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:04,839
What the...?

132
00:08:09,983 --> 00:08:13,920
♪Snow falls upon your sleeves♪

133
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:18,680
♪Yet it cannot conceal
a fate-bound curse♪

134
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:23,480
♪A thousand years of cultivation
were distilled into a single lamp♪

135
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:26,839
Lin Ningxue,

136
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,000
you chose this yourself.

137
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:31,240
Don't blame me then.

138
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,039
Get in the car.

139
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:49,879
Looks like

140
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:51,840
she doesn't recognize me at all.

141
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,320
This is to thank you.

142
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:11,320
Hand over the medicine
and you're free to go.

143
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,799
Ningxue...

144
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:15,480
You may have lost your memories,

145
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,279
don't worry...

146
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:19,440
I will help you get them back.

147
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,759
What are you talking about?

148
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:23,919
It's just the two of us here.

149
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:24,960
Drop the act.

150
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,120
Acting?

151
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,519
You're not sent by Yingying?

152
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,519
Of course not.

153
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:38,159
You get the money, I get the medicine.

154
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:39,759
Medicine?

155
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,120
That's not medicine at all.

156
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:45,360
It won't cure your father.

157
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,120
But I can.

158
00:10:14,017 --> 00:10:18,120
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

159
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:22,840
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

160
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:27,720
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

161
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:32,840
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

162
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:37,240
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

163
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:41,920
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

164
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:47,320
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

165
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:53,400
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

